{"tid":499789,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【#MeToo風暴】紐約警查強姦指控 Hip Hop名人發文標「#NotMe」","createTime":"2017-12-15T07:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T09:17:18.000Z","uid":122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5cc817eb42eec054b49657d04349bf5f3477e7fc","tid":499789,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:53:29.000Z","msg":"美國Hip Hop音樂人西蒙斯（Russell Simmons）周三被3名女性指控強姦後，宣佈將逐一為自己辯護，以證其清白之身。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》周三報道，3名女性稱西蒙斯曾於上世紀80及90年代強姦她們，他本人其後兩度否認指控，而紐約警方周四表示已就案件展開調查。另外，西蒙斯上月亦曾先後被女模特兒Keri Claussen及劇作家Jenny Lumet指控性侵。<br />\n<br />\n西蒙斯周四在網上宣佈：「今天，我將開始好好自辯。我將會毫不猶疑地證明，我在所有強姦指控中均為清白。」<br />\n<br />\n他又在文中加上標記「，並解釋指並非想反對近月令眾多女性公開受性侵經歷的「#MeToo」運動。他表示：「我的目的並非以任何方式抹殺#MeToo運動，而是讓那些指控我的人負起責任。」"},{"pid":"d7c36ed4895c4e74713d1770512516e936b8ca08","tid":499789,"uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.whoateallthepies.tv/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/Luiz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.whoateallthepies.tv%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2011%2F05%2FLuiz.gif&h=7320956b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7696a6080ec331d066255063888d924987a71e53","tid":499789,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:10:37.000Z","msg":"指控教練果個都唔洗負責任<br />\n<br />\n想要指控果個負責任，天方夜譚"},{"pid":"cc75d9f17c202db9dcf06f9b61168933dbcc7921","tid":499789,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:11:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>指控教練果個都唔洗負責任<br />\n<br />\n想要指控果個負責任，天方夜譚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教練告尻學校啦"},{"pid":"960aae07fa566cd8e70f6574259ccb2b1b27ae72","tid":499789,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:14:43.000Z","msg":"老屈0成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a550cd764483013ba2444656ccc75aeed7e011","tid":499789,"uid":5225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T0